    "updated_at": "2025-05-20T19:21:12Z",
    "body": "I agree that changing indices of something like that should be considered a bug, as it would be considered surprising behavior.\n\nBut I also think that behavior shouldn't be dependent on the order of elements in PROMPT_ARRAY...",
